25:40.727 --> 25:43.611
It's not extermination, but a dispossession.

25:44.672 --> 25:51.640
In fact, both words for dispossession and destruction occur not only in Joshua, but throughout the first five books of the Bible.

25:52.060 --> 26:00.370
