26:17.429 --> 26:19.794
Well, they tend to flee.

26:20.738 --> 26:27.449
And there are a number of instances where this appears to be the typical means to which God uses the Israelites to clear the land out before them.

26:27.849 --> 26:32.537
Even the language of total destruction appears to be rhetorical and illustrative.

26:32.617 --> 26:36.843
