26:38.206 --> 26:46.939
And so I think we can read of these instances as references to a total success of the Israelites under Joshua's leadership to inherit the land.

26:47.621 --> 26:48.562
They had been faithful.

26:49.954 --> 26:51.456
Let me attempt to summarize what this means.

26:52.277 --> 26:57.906
