27:04.275 --> 27:08.882
Well, we think it's to kill every man, to kill every woman, and to kill every child.

27:09.730 --> 27:12.673
And I think this confuses the nature of the command to devote to destruction.

27:12.994 --> 27:20.281
But we overemphasize the people being devoted to destruction and underestimate the things being devoted to destruction.

27:21.342 --> 27:30.492
One scholar makes a note that should the cities be mostly in view here, as I think they may be, this is those places where the Israelites focused their destruction.

27:30.512 --> 27:35.858
So this is in contrast to what we might call

27:36.002 --> 27:41.049
the sticks or the rural parts of the land of Canaan.

