28:34.146 --> 28:36.468
I don't think this fully addresses our qualms, does it?

28:37.149 --> 28:37.870
With such a command.

28:38.951 --> 28:52.606
But as we consider God's holiness and justice to execute judgment against sin, let us make sure we're rightly understanding and correctly just what the Lord commanded of Israel in this war to which Israel undertook.

28:54.047 --> 29:00.594
But also, let us be careful not to defang or to declaw God's wrath against sin.

29:03.394 --> 29:09.044
and his utter ability and his utter right to uphold his justice and his just judgments.

29:10.105 --> 29:18.179
