29:39.606 --> 29:43.731
Well, believers, they simply deserved it.

29:44.973 --> 29:48.978
They simply deserved God's just judgment.

29:49.218 --> 30:02.278
God had given them over 400 years to repent and to turn to Yahweh, and yet we only have record of Rahab, and the Gibeonites, though their way isn't necessarily lauded or commended in the Scriptures.

30:03.400 --> 30:06.765
The Canaanites deserved their destruction.

30:08.007 --> 30:12.914
