30:34.894 --> 30:39.762
There would have been a people we would have contacted our elected officials to address and do something about.

30:41.026 --> 30:41.807
And they were people.

30:41.847 --> 30:44.851
The Israelites were to have no part or place.

30:46.293 --> 30:48.255
And so it's not genocide that we have here.

30:48.295 --> 30:55.124
