31:46.526 --> 31:49.050
They deserved it.

31:50.171 --> 31:51.113
But beloved, don't we?

31:52.915 --> 31:53.416
Don't we?

31:53.456 --> 31:56.140
Now, take a breath.

31:56.901 --> 32:00.787
