for he redeems as people.

32:33.185 --> 32:35.328
We see a shadow of Christ suffering.

32:36.910 --> 32:49.107
All right, that just as the judgment of these kings and their people are their deserving end for wickedness, for the wages of sin is death, is this not that to which Jesus himself submitted in our stead?

32:50.629 --> 32:56.978
Have you considered that you and I are deserving of the same fate as the Canaanites or it not for the grace of God?

32:57.570 --> 33:06.015
